{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setUser:"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString","text":"NSString","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"text":"userId","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"emails:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSArray","text":"NSArray","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"text":"emails","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"completion:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"kind":"text","text":" (^"},{"kind":"text","text":")("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSError","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSError"},{"text":" * ","kind":"text"},{"text":"error","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":")) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"completion","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"name":"userId","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The custom user identifier."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"emails","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Array of email address strings.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"completion","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Block called when the operation completes."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Receives nil on success, or an NSError on failure.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Atomically associates a user ID with multiple email addresses and provides"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"confirmation when the operation completes. This is the recommended method","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"for user identification during authentication flows.","type":"text"}]},{"level":2,"text":"Example","anchor":"Example","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Handle OAuth login with full user setup:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["class OAuthLoginHandler {","","    func handleOAuthCallback(_ authResult: OAuthResult,","                            completion: @escaping (Result<Void, Error>) -> Void) {","","        \/\/ Extract user info from OAuth result","        let userId = authResult.userId","        var emails: [String] = []","","        if let primaryEmail = authResult.email {","            emails.append(primaryEmail)","        }","        if let verifiedEmails = authResult.verifiedEmails {","            emails.append(contentsOf: verifiedEmails.filter { $0 != authResult.email })","        }","","        \/\/ Set user and emails with confirmation","        Pushwoosh.configure.setUser(userId, emails: emails) { error in","            if let error = error {","                Logger.error(\"User setup failed: \\(error.localizedDescription)\")","                completion(.failure(error))","                return","            }","","            \/\/ User is now fully identified - set profile tags","            Pushwoosh.configure.setTags([","                \"oauth_provider\": authResult.provider.rawValue,","                \"has_profile_picture\": authResult.profilePictureURL != nil,","                \"locale\": authResult.locale ?? Locale.current.identifier,","                \"first_login\": !self.hasExistingSession(for: userId)","            ])","","            Analytics.track(\"oauth_login_complete\", properties: [","                \"provider\": authResult.provider.rawValue,","                \"email_count\": emails.count","            ])","","            completion(.success(()))","        }","    }","}"]}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setUser:emails:completion:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"sections":[],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setuser:emails:completion:"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"metadata":{"title":"setUser:emails:completion:","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setUser:emails:completion:","kind":"identifier"}],"fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setUser:emails:completion:","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setUser:emails:completion:","symbolKind":"method"},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Sets user identifier and emails with completion handler.","type":"text"}],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","type":"topic","title":"PWConfiguration","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PWConfiguration"}],"abstract":[],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","role":"symbol"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/setUser:emails:completion:":{"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setuser:emails:completion:","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets user identifier and emails with completion handler."}],"title":"setUser:emails:completion:","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setUser:emails:completion:","kind":"identifier"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setUser:emails:completion:"}],"kind":"sy